FBIS4-18551 "drweu067_b_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-067 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 BENELUX COUNTRIES Belgium Foreign Ministry Denounces `Attack' Foreign Ministry Denounces `Attack' LD0704093394 Brussels La Une Radio Network in French 0900 GMT 7 Apr 94 LD0704093394 Brussels La Une Radio Network French BFN [Text] The Ministry of Foreign Affairs has issued a communique on behalf of the Belgian Government. It expresses its shock at last night's brutal attack. These are the Ministry's own words: Belgium strongly condemns a crime which could jeopardize the precarious balance between Rwanda and Burundi.
